(17, 9, 'Publication', NULL, '0', '1', 'https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S2215016120302223', ';', 2, '/scholar?q=info:m8cVyTZW9hUJ:scholar.google.com/&output=cite&scirp=0&hl=en', '/citations?hl=en&xsrf=&continue=/scholar%3Fq%3D%2BGarcia-Avila,%2BF.,%2BSanchez-Alvarracin,%2BC.,%2BCadme-Galabay,%2BM.,%2BConchado-Martinez,%2BJ.,%2BGarcia-Mera,%2BG.,%2BZhindon-Arevalo,%2BC.,%2BRelationship%2Bbetween%2Bchlorine%2Bdecay%2Band%2Btemperature%2Bin%2Bthe%2Bdrinking%2Bwater%2B(2020)%2BMethodsX.,%2B7,%2Bp.%2B101002%26hl%3Den%26as_sdt%3D0,33&citilm=1&json=&update_op=library_add&info=m8cVyTZW9hUJ&ei=8WWTYK7NNMyWywTKnbvACA', '/scholar?cites=1582547112369178523&as_sdt=5,33&sciodt=0,33&hl=en', '/scholar?q=related:m8cVyTZW9hUJ:scholar.google.com/&scioq=+Garcia-Avila,+F.,+Sanchez-Alvarracin,+C.,+Cadme-Galabay,+M.,+Conchado-Martinez,+J.,+Garcia-Mera,+G.,+Zhindon-Arevalo,+C.,+Relationship+between+chlorine+decay+and+temperature+in+the+drinking+water+(2020)+MethodsX.,+7,+p.+101002&hl=en&as_sdt=0,33', 'Relationship between chlorine decay and temperature in the drinking water', 'F García-Ávila;C Sánchez-Alvarracín', 2020, 'MethodsX', 'The bulk chlorine decay rate in drinking water supply systems depend on many factors, including temperature. In this document, the method to determine the order of reaction of chlorine with water is reported, as well as the method to estimate Kb (Bulk reaction rate constant). Experiments were carried out to determine the bulk chlorine decay, for which a set of water samples to determine the free residual chlorine every hour were analyzed. Chlorine concentrations were graphed against time and adjusted appropriately to the developed'),
