(139, 155, 'Publication', NULL, '0', '1', 'https://link.springer.com/article/10.1186/s12939-020-1142-8', ';;', 1, '/scholar?q=info:X049RvAngIUJ:scholar.google.com/&output=cite&scirp=0&hl=en', '/citations?hl=en&xsrf=&continue=/scholar%3Fq%3D%2BBautista-Valarezo,%2BE.,%2BDuque,%2BV.,%2BS%25C3%2583%25C2%25A1nchez,%2BA.E.,%2BD%25C3%2583%25C2%25A1valos-Batallas,%2BV.,%2BMichels,%2BN.R.,%2BHendrickx,%2BK.,%2BVerhoeven,%2BV.,%2BTowards%2Ban%2Bindigenous%2Bdefinition%2Bof%2Bhealth:%2Ban%2Bexplorative%2Bstudy%2Bto%2Bunderstand%2Bthe%2Bindigenous%2BEcuadorian%2Bpeople%25C3%25A2%25E2%2582%25AC%25E2%2584%25A2s%2Bhealth%2Band%2Bi%26hl%3Den%26as_sdt%3D0,33&citilm=1&json=&update_op=library_add&info=X049RvAngIUJ&ei=dXSTYL_vCo3nmQGp8JOQCQ', '/scholar?cites=9619732716987436639&as_sdt=5,33&sciodt=0,33&hl=en', '/scholar?q=related:X049RvAngIUJ:scholar.google.com/&scioq=+Bautista-Valarezo,+E.,+Duque,+V.,+S%C3%83%C2%A1nchez,+A.E.,+D%C3%83%C2%A1valos-Batallas,+V.,+Michels,+N.R.,+Hendrickx,+K.,+Verhoeven,+V.,+Towards+an+indigenous+definition+of+health:+an+explorative+study+to+understand+the+indigenous+Ecuadorian+people%C3%A2%E2%82%AC%E2%84%A2s+health+and+i&hl=en&as_sdt=0,33', 'Towards an indigenous definition of health: an explorative study to understand the indigenous Ecuadorian people\'s health and illness concepts', 'E Bautista-Valarezo;V Duque;AEV Sánchez', 2020, 'International journal for …', 'An intercultural society facilitates equitable and respectful interrelations. Knowing and understanding each other\'s sociocultural and linguitic contexts is a prerequisite for an intercultural society. This study explores the concepts of health and illness among healers of indigenous ethnicities in Southern Ecuador. A qualitative observational study with eleven focus groups was conducted in three locations in Southern Ecuador; a total of 110 participants the Shuar, Kichwa and Mestizo ethnic groups were included. A'),
